title: Mainichi Shine Shine Itte Kuru Gimai ga, Ore ga Neteiru Suki ni Saiminjutsu de Horesaseyou toshite Kuru n desu kedo......!
altTitle: My stepsister who says Go die go die to me every day, tries to hypnotize me to fall for her while I was sleeping...!
毎日死ね死ね言ってくる義妹が、俺が寝ている隙に催眠術で惚れさせようとしてくるんですけど……！
